# Copy to ".env" (or ".env.production") for the frontend build.
#
# In LOCAL development you normally leave this EMPTY: the Vite dev server
# proxies /api to http://localhost:5000 (see vite.config.ts).
#
# In PRODUCTION set it to your deployed backend URL so the built site calls
# the live API directly (no proxy exists in a static build):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://drzouid-api.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=
